A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fyoung-seniors-and-elderly-youths-all-you-need-to-know-about-new-trend-in-china%2Famp_articleshow%2F110465537.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20complete%20guide%20to%20asking%20your%20boss%20for%20a%20sabbatical%2C%20according%20to%20an%20employment%20lawyer%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22738%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20in%20a%20suit%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6650b88d20abc1efe8fd6bac%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22554%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EClaire%20Brooks%20shares%20her%20best%20advice%20for%20workers%20looking%20to%20take%20an%20extended%20break.%3Cp%3EAaron%20%26amp%3B%20Partners%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EClaire%20Brooks%20has%20been%20an%20employment%20partner%20at%20a%20law%20firm%20for%20nearly%2020%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBrooks%20advises%20employers%20in%20everything%20from%20contract%20issues%20to%20complex%20dismissals.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20said%20employees%20should%20emphasise%20how%20a%20sabbatical%20can%C2%A0%20benefit%20the%20business%20and%20be%20reasonable.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20is%20an%20as-told-to%20essay%20based%20on%20a%20transcribed%20conversation%20with%20Claire%20Brooks%2C%20an%20employment%20specialist%20solicitor%20at%20Araon%20and%20Partners%20in%20England.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20sabbatical%20is%20a%20break%20from%20work%2C%20usually%20for%20a%20defined%20time%20period.%20People%20might%20take%20career%20breaks%20to%20pursue%20other%20business%20interests%2C%20participate%20in%20a%20charitable%20initiative%2C%20have%20an%20extended%20holiday%2C%20or%20explore%20the%20world.%20Alternatively%2C%20they%20might%20have%20caring%20responsibilities.%20Ultimately%2C%20it%20could%20be%20for%20any%20reason%20%E2%80%94%20sometimes%20people%20want%20time%20out.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20are%20two%20main%20ways%20of%20doing%20it.%20The%20first%20is%20effectively%20ending%20your%20employment%20with%20the%20option%20to%20return.%20This%20has%20more%20advantages%20for%20an%20employer%2C%20who%20won't%20have%20the%20ongoing%20liability%20of%20an%20employee%20accruing%20length%20of%20service%20and%20retaining%20their%20employment%20rights%20%E2%80%94%20or%20paying%20a%20salary%2C%20holiday%2C%20and%20pension%20%E2%80%94%20while%20the%20employee%20is%20away.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20more%20common%20option%2C%20and%20the%20more%20useful%20for%20an%20employee%2C%20is%20where%20employment%20continues.%20This%20might%20be%20paid%20or%20a%20mixture%20of%20paid%20and%20unpaid%20leave.%20Usually%2C%20these%20kinds%20of%20sabbaticals%20are%20shorter%20%E2%80%93%20between%20three%20and%20six%20months.%20For%20a%20longer%20period%20of%20a%20year%20or%20more%2C%20a%20mutually%20agreed%20termination%20arrangement%20is%20more%20likely.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20career%20break%20has%20advantages%20for%20both%20employees%20and%20employers.%20It%20can%20help%20hardworking%2C%20long-standing%20staff%20avoid%20burnout%2C%20particularly%20where%20their%20work%20is%20very%20intense.%20For%20employers%2C%20it%20can%20be%20hugely%20beneficial%20for%20staff%20well-being%20and%20retention.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fe477e02-da82-4dce-b37c-d5d2a30ec121%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EHow%20to%20request%20a%20sabbatical%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20no%20legal%20entitlement%20to%20a%20sabbatical%2C%20but%20it's%20still%20reasonable%20to%20discuss%20one%20with%20your%20employer.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20no%20rule%20about%20how%20long%20you%20need%20to%20have%20worked%20for%20an%20organization%20before%20requesting%20a%20sabbatical%2C%20but%20they%20are%20generally%20provided%20to%20more%20senior%2C%20long-standing%20staff.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221250325e-d7ca-4dbe-b94a-c78fb8096297%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3ECheck%20whether%20your%20company%20has%20a%20sabbatical%20policy%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20your%20company%20already%20has%20a%20sabbatical%20policy%2C%20you%20should%20follow%20it.%20It%20should%20explain%20the%20eligibility%20requirements%20and%20criteria%20for%20applying%2C%20the%20key%20arrangements%2C%20and%20the%20application%20process.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20there%20isn't%20a%20policy%20in%20place%2C%20employees%20should%20have%20an%20initial%20conversation%20with%20their%20line%20manager%20or%20HR%20to%20determine%20whether%20they%20would%20consider%20it.%20You%20might%20ask%3A%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20were%20open%20to%20considering%20a%20sabbatical%2C%20what%20would%20you%20want%20to%20see%20from%20me%3F%20Is%20there%20anything%20you'd%20like%20to%20see%20me%20demonstrating%20as%20part%20of%20that%20application%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223bd07e8b-929f-437e-9408-3f58f29c8dbf%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EPrepare%20a%20business%20case%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPrepare%20a%20business%20case%20for%20the%20career%20break%20to%20present%20to%20your%20employer.%20Your%20line%20manager%20is%20generally%20the%20best%20person%20to%20have%20this%20conversation%20with.%20Do%20this%20with%20as%20much%20notice%20as%20possible%20to%20give%20them%20the%20opportunity%20to%20think%20about%20it%20and%20decide%20whether%20it's%20something%20they%20can%20support.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EExplain%20what%20you're%20looking%20to%20do%2C%20how%20long%20you'd%20like%20to%20take%20off%2C%20and%20your%20proposal.%20Reassure%20your%20employer%20that%20you're%20asking%20for%20leave%20for%20a%20reason%20they%20can%20support%20and%20that%20it's%20not%20for%20a%20purpose%20that%20might%20cause%20concern%2C%20like%20a%20conflicting%20business%20interest.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShow%20that%20you%20have%20thought%20about%20how%20you'll%20keep%20up%20to%20date%20with%20the%20role%2C%20how%20you'd%20like%20to%20engage%20with%20the%20organization%20while%20you're%20away%2C%20how%20your%20responsibilities%20could%20be%20covered%2C%20and%20how%20you%20see%20the%20return%20to%20the%20role%20afterward.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2298acf1ea-db8f-4409-922b-731019f9698a%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EHighlight%20the%20advantages%20for%20the%20organization%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt's%20useful%20to%20demonstrate%20your%20value%20%E2%80%94%20and%20your%20future%20value.%20Explain%20to%20your%20boss%20how%20the%20sabbatical%20can%20benefit%20them%20upon%20your%20return%2C%20especially%20if%20it's%20being%20funded.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20key%20to%20success%20is%20to%20demonstrate%20the%20potential%20advantages%20for%20the%20organization.%20Find%20out%20what's%20important%20to%20your%20employer%20and%20how%20your%20request%20meets%20their%20aims%20and%20priorities.%20Organizations%20usually%20have%20a%20written%20set%20of%20values%20%E2%80%94%20use%20those%20to%20frame%20your%20request.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22955b07bf-e86a-44c9-b190-794488079c11%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EAim%20high%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYou%20can%20request%20a%20paid%20sabbatical%20in%20the%20first%20instance%20unless%20your%20company%20has%20a%20contrary%20policy%20or%20practice.%20If%20that%20is%20unacceptable%20to%20your%20employer%2C%20consider%20whether%20an%20unpaid%20sabbatical%20would%20work%20for%20you.%20If%20so%2C%20follow%20up%20with%20your%20employer.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EClearly%2C%20a%20paid%20sabbatical%20is%20more%20attractive%20to%20the%20employee%2C%20but%20the%20employer%20may%20be%20more%20willing%20to%20support%20an%20unpaid%20sabbatical%2C%20given%20the%20cost%20to%20the%20company.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e7c84fa5-4f70-419f-8d2f-b185d6ca52ba%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EBe%20willing%20to%20compromise%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20best%20advice%20is%20to%20be%20realistic%20about%20what%20you're%20asking%20for%20and%20willing%20to%20compromise.%20Always%20think%3A%20What%20would%20I%20think%20if%20this%20request%20were%20presented%20to%20me%3F%20Putting%20yourself%20in%20their%20shoes%20will%20help%20you%20put%20together%20a%20more%20reasonable%20request%3A%20one%20which%20sets%20out%20the%20reason%20for%20the%20sabbatical%2C%20how%20it%20will%20help%20you%20and%20your%20employer%20in%20the%20long%20term%20and%20puts%20forward%20a%20sensible%20business%20case%20It%20might%20include%20requesting%20an%20appropriate%20length%20of%20time%20away%2C%20accepting%20a%20combination%20of%20paid%20and%20unpaid%20leave%2C%20or%20not%20receiving%20a%20bonus%20while%20you%20are%20on%20sabbatical.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYou%20can%20still%20negotiate%20with%20your%20employer%20once%20you've%20applied%20for%20a%20sabbatical%2C%20and%20vice%20versa.%20Showing%20reasonableness%20and%20a%20willingness%20to%20negotiate%20will%20help%20to%20reach%20terms%20that%20will%20work%20for%20both%20parties.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2202a30fed-3f65-427d-beac-1a29ad605416%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20happens%20if%20your%20employer%20says%20yes%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20would%20always%20recommend%20that%20a%20sabbatical%20is%20set%20out%20in%20a%20very%20clear%20agreement%20in%20writing%2C%20usually%20drawn%20up%20by%20a%20solicitor.%20A%20properly%20drafted%20agreement%20avoids%20ambiguity%20and%20confusion.%20It%20should%20state%20how%20pay%20will%20work%20%E2%80%94%20including%20pay%20rises%2C%20bonuses%2C%20holiday%20and%20benefits%20%E2%80%94%20just%20like%20any%20other%20form%20of%20leave%20agreement.%20It%20should%20detail%20arrangements%20for%20the%20return%20to%20work%3A%20whether%20the%20employee%20will%20be%20entitled%20to%20return%20to%20their%20role%20and%20the%20circumstances%20under%20which%20they%20would%20be%20offered%20an%20alternative.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20will%20also%20need%20a%20termination%20provision%20explaining%20what%20notice%20the%20employee%20would%20be%20required%20to%20give%20if%20they%20didn't%20return%20to%20work%20and%20any%20clawback%20provisions%20%E2%80%94%20which%20might%20require%20the%20employee%20to%20repay%20any%20money%20or%20the%20value%20of%20any%20benefits%20they%20receive%20%E2%80%94%20in%20place.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt's%20important%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20employees%20maintain%20contact%20and%20update%20their%20contact%20information%20while%20they%20are%20away%2C%20too.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ef8f120e-32d8-4744-8408-b292f7ed0b16%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20if%20it's%20a%20no%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EConsider%20alternatives%20like%20flexible%20or%20part-time%20work.%20Since%206%20April%20this%20year%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhelptogrow.campaign.gov.uk%2Fflexible-working%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eany%20employee%20has%20the%20right%20to%20make%20a%20flexible%20working%20application%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20from%20day%20one%2C%20regardless%20of%20how%20long%20they%20have%20been%20employed%20at%20their%20organization.%20If%20you%20want%20to%20go%20part-time%20or%20have%20a%20regular%20volunteering%20day%2C%20for%20any%20reason%2C%20you%20can%20make%20the%20request.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20think%20employers%20are%20increasingly%20open%20to%20flexibility%2C%20and%20I%20would%20advise%20them%20to%20consider%20employee%20requests%20with%20an%20open%20mind.%20If%20requests%20are%20taken%20seriously%2C%20employers%20can%20maintain%20trust%20in%20a%20