%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20broker%20told%20CNN%20Money.%20%26quot%3BIt%20has%20three%20engines%2C%20so%20it%20would%20cost%20about%20%2410%2C000%20an%20hour%20to%20fly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20has%20to%20be%20a%20specific%20person%20who%20wants%20that%20plane%20%E2%80%94%20someone%20who%20wants%20it%20because%20it%20belonged%20to%20Donald%20Trump.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBefore%20the%20727%20was%20his%20personal%20plane%2C%20it%20was%20part%20of%20the%20'Trump%20Shuttle'%20fleet%20%E2%80%94%20a%20now-defunct%20US%20carrier%20that%20the%20ex-president%20owned%20until%201992.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Trump%20Shuttle%20Landing%20at%20National%20Airport%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F664f4442a961b37edf392130%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22677%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETrump%20Shuttle%20eventually%20became%20American%20Airlines%20Shuttle%20via%20mergers.%20The%20brand%20ended%20in%202021%20due%20to%20COVID-19.%3Cp%3EBettmann%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20bought%20a%20US%20airline%20called%20Eastern%20Air%20Shuttle%20and%20its%2017%20Boeing%20727s%20in%201988%20for%20%24365%20million%2C%20according%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Farchive%2Fpolitics%2F1988%2F10%2F13%2Ftrump-buys-easterns-air-shuttle%2F1ea719e9-6bc4-48b2-bc12-141351124d0a%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWashington%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E%20article%20from%20the%20same%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20vision%20turned%20the%20initially%20no-frills%20operation%20into%20a%20luxury%20carrier%2C%20outfitting%20the%20planes%20with%20luxe%20interiors%2C%20inflight%20calling%2C%20and%20free%20meals%20and%20drinks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20plan%20worked%20for%20a%20while%2C%20but%20the%20high%20operating%20costs%20weren't%20sustainable%2C%20and%20Trump%20Shuttle%20came%20under%20US%20Airways%20in%201992%20and%20eventually%20%3C