6quot%3Bour%20approval%20was%20not%20taken...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20has%20been%20going%20on%20for%20two-and-a-half%20years%20(referring%20to%20the%20Rajkot%20gaming%20zone).%20Are%20we%20to%20assume%20you%20turned%20a%20blind%20eye%3F%20What%20do%20you%20and%20your%20followers%20do%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20thundered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Rajkot%20gaming%20zone%2C%20it%20has%20emerged%2C%20was%20granted%20a%20license%20by%20local%20cops%20in%20November%20last%20year%2C%20which%20was%20renewed%20to%20December%2031%2C%202024%2C%20Rajkot%20Police%20Commissioner%20Raju%20Bhargava%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hearing%20then%20went%20from%20bad%20to%20worse%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Frajkot%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERajkot%3C%2Fa%3E%20municipal%20body%20after%20photographs%20showed%20officials%20at%20the%20gaming%20zone.%20%26quot%3BWho%20were%20these%20officers%3F%20Did%20they%20go%20there%20to%20play%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frajkot-game-zone-fire-gujarat-high-court-cant-run-game-zone-at-cost-of-small-children-being-killed-high-court-5755909%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BCan't%20Run%20Game%20Zone%20At%20Cost%20Of%20Children%20Being%20Killed%26quot%3B%3A%20Court%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20ripped%20into%20the%20state%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHave%20you%20gone%20blind%3F%20Did%20you%20fall%20asleep%3F%20Now%20we%20do%20not%20trust%20the%20local%20system%20and%20the%20state%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20raged%20when%20told%20fire%20safety%20certification%20hearings%20have%20been%20unresolved%20for%20four%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdvocate%20Manisha%20Luv%20Kumar%20Shah%2C%20appearing%20for%20the%20state%20government%2C%20also%20acknowledged%20that%20two%20other%20gaming%20zones%20-%20in%2