%20Kumar's%20counsel%20said%20they%20have%20filed%20a%20trespassing%20complaint%20against%20Ms%20Maliwal.%20%26quot%3BShe%20directly%20entered%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20residence.%20This%20amounts%20to%20trespass.%20This%20is%20a%20Chief%20Minister's%20home%2C%20can%20anyone%20come%20like%20this%3F%20She%20was%20asked%20to%20wait%20outside%2C%20but%20she%20barged%20and%20crossed%20the%20security%20zone.%20Being%20an%20MP%20gives%20you%20the%20licence%20to%20do%20anything.%20This%20is%20trespass%2C%20and%20the%20FIR%20is%20against%20us.%20What%20kind%20of%20investigation%20is%20this%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQuestioning%20who%20had%20asked%20her%20to%20visit%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20residence%2C%20Bibhav%20Kumar's%20counsel%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BShe%20came%20with%20something%20in%20her%20mind%2C%20she%20had%20premeditated%20thoughts%20before%20coming.%20She%20kept%20asking%20security%20personnel%20if%20they%20had%20spoken%20to%20Bibhav%20Kumar.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Ms%20Maliwal%20barged%20in%2C%20Bibhav%20Kumar%20asked%20the%20security%20personnel%20why%20she%20was%20allowed%20in%2C%20his%20counsel%20asked.%20%26quot%3BHe%20has%20to%20ask%2C%20as%20he%20is%20answerable%20for%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20security.%20Security%20personnel%20then%20went%20inside%20and%20with%20all%20respect%2C%20she%20was%20escorted%20outside.%20She%20was%20walking%20out%20of%20the%20place%20normally.%20There%20was%20no%20hesitation%20seen%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawyer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBibhav%20Kumar's%20counsel%20also%20questioned%20the%20delay%20in%20Ms%20Maliwal%20filing%20a%20police%20complaint.%20%26quot%3BShe%20did%20not%20file%20any%20complaint%20that%20day.%20She%20did%20it%20three%20days%20later.%20She%20was%20the%20DCW%20chief%2C%20she%20was%20well%20aware%20of%20her%20rights.%20If%20her%20rights%20were%20violated%2C%20she%20should%20have%20filed%20the%20complaint%20immediately.%20Why%20the%20delay%20of%20three%20days%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawyer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBibhav%20Kumar's%20counsel%20also%20questioned%20what%20the%20motive%20behind%20the%20alleged%20offences%20is.%20%26quot%3BLook%20at%20the%20place%20where%20the%20incident%20is%20happening%2C%20so%20many%20people%20are%20there.%20The%20protocol%20officer%20is%20there%2C%20the%20security%20officer%20is%20there%20and%20everyone%20knows%20that%20Swati%20Maliwal%20called%20Bibhav%20Kumar.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lawyer%20also%20questioned%20police's%20decision%20to%20add%20the%20IPC%20section%20relating%20to%20an%20intent%20to%20disrobe%20a%20woman.%20%26quot%3BThere%20was%20no%20intent%20to%20disrobe%20her.%20The%20only%20intent%20was%20to%20prevent%20her%20from%20entering%20the%20CM's%20residence.%20The%20allegations%20levelled%20do%20not%20show%20that%20there%20was%20an%20intent%20to%20disrobe%20her.%20All%20that%20can%20be%20seen%20is%20that%20during%20the%20scuffle%2C%20her%20shirt%20was%20torn.%20It%20is%20an%20incidental%20situation%20that%20has%20happened.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20entire%20FIR%2C%20Bibhav%20Kumar's%20counsel%20said%2C%20is%20an%20%26quot%3Bafterthought%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20only%20seeking%20bail.%20I%20am%20not%20seeking%20acquittal%20or%20discharge%20but%20bail.%20Everything%20was%20preplanned%20to%20suit%20the%20story.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20one%20point%20during%20the%20hearing%2C%20Ms%20Maliwal%20started%20crying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpposing%20Bibhav%20Kumar's%20request%20for%20bail%2C%20Delhi%20Police's%20counsel%20said%20no%20intent%20is%20required%20in%20this%20case.%20%26quot%3BYou%20are%20beating%20a%20lady%20alone%20without%20any%20provocation.%20She%20was%20dragged.%20You%20were%20beating%20a%20lady%20in%20such%20a%20manner%20that%20buttons%20opened...%20here%20intention%20is%20not%20required%2C%20what%20you%20are%20doing%20may%20outrage%20modesty%20and%20that%20has%20to%20be%20seen.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20Police's%20lawyer%20responded