ailure%20on%20part%20of%20the%20ECI%20in%20due%20time%20this%20court%20is%20constrained%20to%20pass%20an%20injunction%20order%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Bhattacharya%20said%20in%20his%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20Commission%20sent%20a%20notice%20to%20the%20state%20BJP%20chief%20Sukanta%20Majumdar%2C%20questioning%20why%20the%20ads%20should%20not%20be%20considered%20a%20violation%20of%20the%20Model%20Code.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716798720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F9ijrm348_supreme-court_625x300_15_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-vs-tmc-lok-sabha-elections-rival-not-enemy-supreme-court-junks-bjp-plea-over-ads-against-tmc-5754743%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20refused%20dismissed%20a%20petition%20-%20filed%20by%20the%20BJP%20-%20that%20challenged%20the%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%20order%20restarining%20the%20party%20to%20publish%20%26quot%3Bderogatory%26quot%3B%20advertisements%20targetting%20Bengal's%20ruling%20Trinamool%20Congress.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-vs-tmc-lok-sabha-elections-rival-not-enemy-supreme-court-junks-bjp-plea-over-ads-against-tmc-5754743%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-vs-tmc-lok-sabha-elections-rival-not-enemy-supreme-court-junks-bjp-plea-over-ads-against-tmc-5754743%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-vs-tmc-lok-sabha-elections-rival-not-enemy-supreme-court-junks-bjp-plea-over-ads-against-tmc-5754743%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Miss%20USA%20Savannah%20Gankiewicz%20Receives%20Death%20Threats%20Amid%20Pageant%20Controversy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESavannah%20Gankiewicz%20from%20Hawaii%20was%20crowned%20Miss%20USA%202023%20a%20few%20days%20ago%20after%20the%20previous%20title%20holder%20resigned%20citing%20her%20mental%20health.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fsavannah-gankiewicz-crowned-miss-usa-after-previous-winner-suddenly-resigned-5677368%5C%22%3EMs%20Gankiewicz%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20hold%20the%20title%20till%20August%20this%20year%2C%20the%20remainder%20of%20the%20pageant's%20term.%20Amid%20this%2C%20the%2028-year-old%20said%20that%20she%20has%20received%20death%20threats%20and%20hateful%20messages%20since%20taking%20the%20crown%2C%20as%20per%20a%20report%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcnews.com%2Fnews%2Fus-news%2Fmiss-usa-savannah-gankiewicz-says-received-death-threats-hateful-messa-rcna154048%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENBC%20News%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSince%20I've%20gotten%20this%20title%2C%20I've%20dealt%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20bullying%20and%20harassment%2C%20and%20it%20really%20does%2C%20it%20breaks%20my%20heart%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Gankiewicz%20said%20in%20a%20video%20shared%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20wiping%20away%20her%20tears%2C%20she%20continued%2C%20%26quot%3BSorry.%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20cry%2C%20but%20I%20just%20feel%20like%20it's%20hard%2C%20because%20I%20wish%20people%20saw%20where%20my%20heart%20is%20coming%20from.%20And%20it's%20helping%20Lahaina%20and%20helping%20Maui%20residents%20and%20having%20a%20platform%2C%20but%20also%20showing%20young%20women%20that%20you%20can%20get%20bullied%20and%20you%20can%20hurt%20but%20you%20stand%20back%20up%20and%20you%20keep%20going%20and%20you%20keep%20using%20your%20voice.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hawaiian%20has%20taken%20over%20the%20title%20from%20Noelia%20Voigt%2C%20who%20resigned%20on%20May%206.%20Ms%20Voigt%20had%20shared%20the%20news%20in%20an%20Instagram%20post.%20%26quot%3BI%20realise%20this%20may%20come%20as%20a%20large%20shock%20to%20many.%20Never%20compromise%20your%20physical%20and%20mental%20well-being%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote%20in%20the%20caption.%20Ms%20V