-mango-guava-on-terrace-gardening-indian-flowers-sushma-reddy-bengaluru%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Love%20Keeps%20Me%20Going%E2%80%99%3A%20Why%20This%2084-YO%20Grandma%20Sells%20Idlis%20for%20Just%20Rs%202%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20me%2C%20what%20matters%20most%20is%20to%20see%20my%20customers%20leaving%20with%20a%20full%20stomach%20and%20a%20smile.%20We%20are%20here%20on%20this%20earth%20for%20a%20few%20years%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20not%20run%20behind%20money.%20Love%20keeps%20me%20going%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dhanam.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20you%20enter%20Dhanam%20%3Cem%3EPaati%20%3C%2Fem%3E(grandmother)%E2%80%99s%20house%20in%20Pudukkottai%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20you%20will%20find%20people%20across%20different%20age%20groups%20sitting%20down%20in%20anticipation%20of%20hot%20platefuls%20of%20%3Cem%3Eidlis%2C%20chutney%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20%3Cem%3Esambhar.%20%3C%2Fem%3EYou%20see%2C%20this%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F334919%2Fchiblu-idlis-in-bamboo-bengaluru-babu-hotel-halaguru-village-in-karnataka%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Eidli%20%3C%2Fem%3Eshop%3C%2Fa%3E%20may%20not%20have%20chairs%20or%20tables%2C%20or%20a%20fancy%20entrance%2C%20but%20what%20it%20has%20in%20abundance%20are%20ladlefuls%20of%20the%20octogenarian%E2%80%99s%20love.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mud%20house%2C%20held%20together%20by%20tarpaulin%20sheets%20and%20a%20thatched%20roof%20is%20a%20place%20where%20schoolchildren%2C%20daily-wage%20workers%20and%20office%20goers%20gather%20every%20morning%20to%20have%20a%20scrumptious%20breakfast%20that%20keeps%20them%20full%20till%20afternoon%20or%20more.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20needs%20to%20duck%20down%20to%20enter%20the%20house%2C%20which%20also%20doubles%20up%20as%20the%20shop.%20Customers%20sit%20down%20on%20the%20mud%20floor.%20The%20highlight%2C%20and%20what%20keeps