mage-350413%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EGanesh%20has%20been%20committed%20to%20organic%20farming%20at%20the%20homestay%20since%202002%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Ganesh%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20Ganesh%E2%80%99s%20mangoes%20make%20their%20way%20to%20markets%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20Thane%2C%20Kolhapur%2C%20Sangli%2C%20Nashik%2C%20and%20Pune.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%20that%20while%20they%20did%20try%20their%20hands%20out%20at%20other%20vegetables%2C%20growing%20mangoes%20seemed%20the%20most%20lucrative%20option.%20%E2%80%9CAside%20from%20the%20demand%20for%20mangoes%2C%20there%20are%20other%20factors%20that%20make%20them%20suitable%20for%20us%20to%20grow.%20When%20we%20tried%20growing%20vegetables%2C%20cows%20would%20eat%20them%2C%20and%20we%20did%20not%20have%20money%20to%20hire%20people%20who%20would%20keep%20a%20watch%20on%20the%20fields.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThus%20the%20family%20decided%20to%20channel%20their%20energies%20into%20mangoes.%20And%20it%20is%20a%20bonus%20that%20Ratnagiri%E2%80%99s%20prowess%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F347512%2Forder-mangoes-ratnagiri-devgadh-alphonso-jardalu-online-in-mumbai-bengaluru-delhi-pune%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAlphonso%20mangoes%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20GI-tag%20proof.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reason%20for%20Ratnagiri%20being%20hailed%20as%20the%20best%20for%20Alphonso%20mangoes%2C%20Ganesh%20says%2C%20is%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20laterite%20soil%20here.%20%E2%80%9CAdd%20to%20this%20the%20favourable%20climate!%E2%80%9D%20He%20emphasises%20that%20the%20mangoes%20he%20sells%20are%20genuine%20and%20have%20a%20unique%20identity.%20The%20Alphonso%20mango%20has%20long%20since%20worn%20the%20crown%20for%20being%20one%20of%20the%20sweetest%2C%20most%20aromatic%20varieties%2C%20named%20after%20Portuguese%20general%20and%